H0.text: Ligaments, together with bones and cartilage, make up the skeletal system.

H1.text: Muscles make up the skeletal system together with bones and cartilage.

H2.text: Organs make up the skeletal system along with bones and cartilage.

H3.text: Lungs make up the skeletal system together with bones and cartilage.

A4.text: These are all found in the skeletal system of the human body.
